ANTIPHON
Barely, with a lot of text. Granma was born in 1925. Father was born to granma in 1950. Mother was born in 1951. My brother was born to father and mother in 1987. I was born to them in 1990. I find it hard to explain the larger family without an interface.

SOFIA
